---
<section class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-6 pt-20 overflow-hidden">

  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 h-full w-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-950">
    <div class="absolute h-full w-full
      /* Light Mode: Garis abu-abu lebih kontras (opacity 0.15) */
      bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808026_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808026_1px,transparent_1px)]

      /* Dark Mode: Biru Neon Halus (opacity 0.2) */
      dark:bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#3b82f633_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#3b82f633_1px,transparent_1px)]

      bg-[size:60px_60px]
      [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_50%_at_50%_0%,#000_70%,transparent_100%)]">
    </div>

    <div class="absolute inset-0 dark:bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_0%,rgba(59,130,246,0.05)_0%,transparent_50%)]"></div>
  </div>

  <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" class="z-10">
    <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-blue-400 rounded-full mb-6 border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800">
      Fullstack Developer
    </span>
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-tight">
      Menghidupkan <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r px-4 from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 dark:from-blue-400 dark:to-cyan-300">Ide</span><br />Lewat <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r px-4 from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 dark:from-blue-400 dark:to-cyan-300">Baris Kode.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl mb-10 mx-auto font-medium">
      Mengubah logika sistem yang kompleks menjadi pengalaman digital yang <span class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white underline decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-4 font-bold">intuitif, bersih, dan modern</span>.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="#proyek" class="px-8 py-4 bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white dark:text-slate-950 text-white rounded-2xl font-bold hover:-translate-y-1 transition shadow-xl shadow-blue-500/10">Lihat Proyek</a>
      <a href="#skills" class="px-8 py-4 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 rounded-2xl font-bold hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-900 transition text-sm">Teknologi</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
